data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable Santana Ranch community of Hollister, CA! This stunning listing offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality, making it an ideal choice for those seeking an exceptional living experience. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this spacious home features an inviting open floor plan that's perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The recently remodeled kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with modern finishes and top-of-the-line appliances, making hosting gatherings a breeze.Step into the elegantly remodeled bathrooms, where luxury and relaxation await. The high ceilings throughout the home create an airy and expansive atmosphere. 3-car tandem garage, you'll have ample space for vehicles and storage. And don't forget to take advantage of the breathtaking sunsets that grace your back yard each evening.  Families will appreciate being situated within a great school district, ensuring quality education for your loved ones. Plus, the addition of a new park nearby offers endless opportunities for outdoor recreation and leisure. This listing in the Santana Ranch community of Hollister, CA is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade. Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property your very own.
